Preconditions:
- The input array `groupSizes` is not null.
- The input array `groupSizes` contains at least one element.

Postconditions:
- The returned list of groups is not null.
- The returned list of groups contains at least one element.
- Each person appears in exactly one group.
- Every person is in a group.
- The size of each group in the returned list matches the corresponding value in the `groupSizes` array.